xplanation": "Yes! The answer is \"I like walk, skip, and hop.\"."}, {"type": "explain", "title": "You've got this!", "body": "Great work learning about Commas in a List! Now tap a worksheet to practice and earn points. You can always come back to this lesson."}]$tl$::jsonb
